        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">This is the Europan production capacity in 2000 (HERA, 2004). According to HERA about 400 million kg of those 600 million kg are consumed in Europe, the rest is exported. The global production is estimated to be 3 billion tonnes, whereby the shares among production technologies are distributed as follows: 80% HF, 10% AlCl3, and 10% fixed-bed (HERA, 2004).

Reference(s):
Human and Environmental Risk Assessment (HERA). 2004. LAS - Linear Alkylbenzene Sulphonate (CAS No. 68411-30-3), Version 2.0. pp. 8-9. Report retreived online from http://wko.at/up/enet/stellung/qualitaetszielstellbeilage2.pdf, 4 July 2017.</productionVolumeComment>
